Class QSqlDriver.DriverFeature

Enclosing class:
QSqlDriver
public static final class QSqlDriver.DriverFeature
extends java.lang.Enum
implements QtEnumerator

This enum contains a list of features a driver might support. Use hasFeature() to query whether a feature is supported or not. More information about supported features can be found in the Qt SQL driver documentation.

See also:
hasFeature().

QuerySize

public static final QSqlDriver.DriverFeature QuerySize
Whether the database is capable of reporting the size of a query. Note that some databases do not support returning the size (i.e. number of rows returned) of a query, in which case QSqlQuery::size() will return -1.
